"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Προβολή</guimenu> <guimenuitem>View Frame Source</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (Browser mode)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2979
#, no-c-format
msgid "View frame source text"
