"φορτώνεται κατά την εκκίνηση;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konqueror; has a <guilabel>Home Folder</guilabel> used in file manager mode "
"and a <guilabel>Home Page</guilabel> used in browser mode."
